    <p><strong>Transitive, intransitive and linking verbs</strong></p>
    <h3>A. Study the examples.</h3>
    <p>A couple bought a couple of tickets for their honeymoon.<br>
        The car stopped suddenly. <br>
        All the children seem satisfied with their exam result. <br>
