    <h3>d. The word superstition is derived from the Latin supersisto. It means &quot;;to stand in terror of the Deity&quot;.</h3>
    <p><strong>Ans: </strong>Superstition is a belief in the magical &amp; supernatural powers. It is mostly based on myths or pseudo
