    <h2>Ways with Words</h2>
    <h3>A. Find the words from the text which mean the following. The first letter has been given.</h3>
    <p>
    <ol type="a">
        <li>making you feel physically relaxed; pleasant to wear, sit on, etc. - <u>comfortable</u> </li>
        <li>having a degree from the university - <u>graduating</u> </li>
        <li>without being connected with or influenced by something or by each other - <u>independently</u> </li>
        <li>the introduction of new things, ideas or ways of doing something - <u>innovation</u> </li>
        <li>familiar with something, having read, seen or experienced it - <u>acquainted</u></li>
        <li>a person who makes money by starting or running businesses, especially when this involves taking financial
            risks - <u>entrepreneur</u> </li>
        <li>an opportunity or a place for somebody to express their opinions publicly or make progress in a particular
