    <h2>Ways with word</h2>
    <h3>A. Match the words on the left side with their meanings on the right.</h3>
    <p>
        a. proclaim ----------------------v. declare<br>
        b. unswerving -------------------iv. steady or constant<br>
        c. magnanimous ----------------i. generous or forgiving<br>
        d. trample ------------------------x. crush<br>
        e. tremendous -------------------vii. huge<br>
        f. inevitable -----------------------ix. unavoidable<br>
        g. dire ------------------------------iii. dreadful<br>
        h. anguish -------------------------ii. distress<br>
