    <p>&emsp;&emsp;What Lost Identity? The Diaspora and Globalisation</p>
    <h2>Before you read</h2>
    <h3>a. Why do you think people leave their home countries? </h3>
    <p><strong>Ans: </strong>People leave their home countries in search of better employment opportunities and
