        resources, she and her family have to live very unhappy life. As she has to spend most of her time earning
        wages, her children are not properly looked after. The poor babies have to do with cornbread without eggs. and
        oleo. She even does not have a material to attend her children with runny noses. They don't have extra books, no
        magazines, no extra pencils, or crayons, or paper and most important of all, they do not have health. They have
        worms and infections. They do not sleep well on the floor. Similarly, other children don't play with them.</p>
