        no matter how long she waits, she is sent home without any reward.</p>
    <h3>d. Why are people's opinions and prejudices her greatest obstacles?</h3>
    <p><strong>Ans: </strong>According to Parker, the upper and middle classes cannot understand her situation. Instead
