        poverty. Instead, they will join the gang of thieves. She imagines them behind the

        bars of their prison. They will start using drug or alcohol to forget the pain of

        enslavement and unemployment. She expresses bitterness at the thought of her

        daughter leading a hellish life, like hers.
    </p>
