    </p>


<h3>g. What is the final judgment on Waserkopf's demand of refund? </h3>
<p>Waserkopf's demand of refund is overruled as he succeeds in the re-examination
    conducted by his old school teachers.
    </p>

<h2>Reference to the context</h2>
